data.name: label2.ToolTip
data.value: How many parts of those defined above will be used to generate password. Default is 0, which means no limit. For example, if you defined the parts "Correct Horse Battery Staple" and you selected a maximum of 2, the program will test "Correct Staple", "Horse Battery" and others, but never "Correct Staple Battery" and those over 2 parts
